title: My relay recently got the Guard flag and traffic dropped by half.
---
description:

Since it's now a guard, clients are using it less in other positions, but not many clients have rotated their existing guards out to use it as a guard yet. Read more details in this [blog post](https://blog.torproject.org/blog/lifecycle-of-a-new-relay) or in [Changing of the Guards: A Framework for Understanding and Improving Entry Guard Selection in Tor](http://freehaven.net/anonbib/#wpes12-cogs). 
